---
description: Never add Cursor co-author trailers to git commits
alwaysApply: true
---

Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` / `cursoragent@cursor.com` / `@cursor.com` / `Made-with: Cursor` trailers to git commits in this repository.

When creating commits:
- Do not pass Cursor co-author trailers to `git commit`
- Prefer repository hooks via `make setup-hooks` (`.githooks/`)
- If a trailer appears, strip it before push; use `make check-no-cursor-coauthor`
